\begin_inset Formula 
\[
f_{X}(x|\mu,\sigma)=\frac{1}{\sigma}\frac{63}{4}\left(\left(\frac{x-\mu}{\sigma}\right)^{6}-\left(\frac{x-\mu}{\sigma}\right)^{8}\right)
\]

\end_inset

Then
