\frac{1}{2}\frac{\sqrt{v}}{\sqrt{u}} & \frac{1}{2}\frac{\sqrt{u}}{\sqrt{v}}\\
\frac{1}{2}\frac{1}{\sqrt{u}\sqrt{v}} & -\frac{1}{2}\frac{\sqrt{u}}{\sqrt{v}v}
\end{array}\right)\right|\right\Vert =\left\Vert -\frac{1}{4}\frac{1}{v}-\frac{1}{4}\frac{1}{v}\right\Vert =\frac{1}{2v}
