 Then
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
f_{Y}(y)=\binom{n}{y}\int_{0}^{1}\left(1-x\right)^{y}x^{n-y}dx=\binom{n}{y}\frac{\Gamma\left(n-y+1\right)\Gamma(y+1)}{\Gamma\left(n+2\right)}=\frac{1}{n+1}
\]

